6. maytrexanh.com
7. longdengiasi.com

## What to KEEP from WP
- post_type: post, page, product
- All slugs (never change without 301)
- Featured images (rewrite URL to R2)
- Categories + tags
- SEO meta (Yoast: title, desc, focus keyword)
- Schema JSON-LD

## What to DISCARD from WP
- shop_orders, attachments, nav_menu_item, amp_validated_url, wp_global_styles
- WP shortcodes: [gallery], [caption], [vc_row], [vc_column], all [/*] tags
- WP block comments: <!-- wp:... --> <!-- /wp:... -->
- Elementor/Visual Composer markup
- WP sidebar widgets
- WP comments

## Standard per-site flow
1. Parse XML → audit counts (wp-xml-to-postgres skill).
2. Upload media to R2 (r2-upload-and-verify skill).
3. Clone longdenviet skeleton + apply brand (site-brand-apply skill).
4. Import data to Postgres (postgres-import-audit skill).
5. Test localhost (content/slug/image/mobile).
6. Deploy Oracle staging.
7. Run pre-launch checks (site-launch-checklist skill).
8. Cut over Vultr + Cloudflare DNS (staging-to-production-cutover skill).

## Pre-live checklist
- Critical 404 issues = 0.
- Redirects verified.
- Sitemap and robots valid.
- Images load correctly.
- GA/GSC verification completed.

